---
title: "update-frontend-docs — Refresh a single area of the frontend analysis + regenerate affected .claude/ artefacts"
---
%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Claude
    participant SA as Subagent(s)
    participant FS as File System

    User->>Claude: /update-frontend-docs <area> [--all-frontends]

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Preflight
    Claude->>Claude: START_TS = date +%s
    Claude->>FS: Read .claude/state/frontend-analysis.json
    FS-->>Claude: JSON / not found

    alt JSON not found
        Claude->>User: No frontend analysis found.<br/>Run /analyze-frontend first<br/>(then /create-frontend-docs).
        break Skill aborts
            Claude->>User: Aborted
        end
    end

    alt schema_version mismatch
        Claude->>User: Schema mismatch.<br/>Re-run /analyze-frontend to regenerate.
        break Skill aborts
            Claude->>User: Aborted
        end
    end

    alt <area> missing or invalid
        Claude->>User: Which area to refresh?<br/>[1] design-system    — tokens, CSS vars, theme<br/>[2] components       — inventory + conventions<br/>[3] data-flow        — state, API, auth, forms<br/>[4] architecture     — folder layout, routing, SSR<br/>[5] framework-idioms — idiomatic patterns<br/>[6] feature-flows    — user-facing feature patterns<br/>[7] template         — reassemble template from current JSON
        User-->>Claude: number or area name
    end

    note over Claude,User: Phase: Scope resolution
    opt frontend_roots.length > 1
        alt --all-frontends flag set
            Claude->>Claude: Scope = all frontend_roots
        else no flag
            Claude->>User: N frontends found. Which to refresh?<br/>[1] <root-1> (main frontend)<br/>[2] <root-2><br/>...<br/>[A] All frontends
            User-->>Claude: number(s) or A
        end
    end

    alt area == "template"
        note over Claude,SA: Skip subagent — template-only reassembly from JSON
    else area != "template"
        note over Claude,SA: Phase: Re-invoke subagent(s)
        loop For each in-scope frontend
            Claude->>SA: Invoke subagent(s) for <area><br/>with fresh stack_profile + entry_points
            SA-->>Claude: ## Summary Row + ## Artefact
        end

        Claude->>User: Diff preview (old JSON section vs new):<br/>  + added lines  - removed lines<br/>[1] Accept and continue<br/>[2] Skip this frontend<br/>[3] Cancel
        User-->>Claude: choice

        note over Claude,FS: Phase: Update JSON
        Claude->>FS: Read current frontend-analysis.json
        FS-->>Claude: content
        Claude->>Claude: Replace frontend_roots[i].<area-key>.<br/>Update generated.ts to now.
        Claude->>FS: Atomic write frontend-analysis.json
        FS-->>Claude: OK
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Regenerate artefact
    Claude->>User: Artefact to write:<br/>  <path>  ~N lines (was M lines)<br/>[1] Write (default)<br/>[2] Skip
    User-->>Claude: choice

    alt area == "design-system"
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/rules/frontend-design-system.md
    else area == "components"
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/rules/frontend-components.md +<br/>.claude/docs/reference-component-inventory.md
    else area == "data-flow"
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/sequences/frontend-data-flow.mmd
    else area == "architecture"
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/docs/reference-architecture-frontend.md +<br/>update Stack section in reference-component-creation-template.md
    else area == "framework-idioms"
        Claude->>FS: Update ## Framework-specific idioms in<br/>reference-component-creation-template.md
    else area == "feature-flows"
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/sequences/features/<pattern>.mmd +<br/>update ## Feature data flows in template
    else area == "template"
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/docs/reference-component-creation-template.md
    end
    FS-->>Claude: OK

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Update CLAUDE.md (conditional)
    opt area in {architecture, framework-idioms, template}
        Claude->>FS: Read root CLAUDE.md
        FS-->>Claude: content
        Claude->>Claude: Refresh Stack line + cross-refs in ### Frontend
        Claude->>FS: Write updated CLAUDE.md
        FS-->>Claude: OK
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Report
    Claude->>Claude: END_TS = date +%s<br/>wall_clock_sec = END_TS - START_TS
    Claude->>FS: Write .claude/state/reports/<br/>update-frontend-docs-DISPLAY_TS.md
    FS-->>Claude: OK

    Claude->>User: Dashboard:<br/>Area: <area> · Frontends: N · Artefacts: M<br/>Duration: S seconds · Report path<br/>Next: /create-frontend-docs if template area changed
